0.9.0.name: wordpress/my-library
0.9.0.description:
My Library allows you to feature books you've read and are currently reading via a side-bar widget and shortcodes that can be embedded in pages or posts. You can also rate them and the books will link to Amazon.com using your affiliate tag.

Questions/Comments/Suggestions welcome.
